Data Scientist / Algorithmic Solutions - Programmatic Media (NYC)		Accordant Media		Greater New York City Area		<div class="rich-text" itemprop="description"><p><strong> </strong> </p><p>The <strong>Data Scientist</strong>is a member of Accordant's Analytics and Insights department and acts as the lead advocate for innovation, execution and delivery of Accordant Media’s algorithmic data and artificial intelligence capabilities across multiple digital media channels and tactics. </p><p></p><p>The Data Scientist will contribute to the ongoing development of Accordant’s machine learning algorithms and real time analytic solutions. This role will work closely with Accordant’s Engineering, Product, Analytics and Client Service groups to facilitate the implementation of real time analytics within the Accordant product suite. This individual will be responsible for ensuring that the algorithms utilize cutting edge methodologies while maintaining stability and transparency. </p><p></p><p><strong>Specific Responsibilities and Activities</strong> </p><ul><li>Quickly develop a fundamental understanding of the techniques and methodologies used for the implementation of the real time analytic solutions in place, and the currently-planned development roadmap </li><li>Develop additional solutions to monitor performance of current tools and implement enhancements to improve scalability, reliability, and performance </li><li>Working with senior leadership to communicate current status and future development plans for the analytic product suite </li><li>Remain aware of the latest machine learning and predictive analytic practices and methodologies </li><li>Create supporting documentation for algorithms and models </li><li>Act as a subject matter expert on machine learning, for both internal and external audiences </li><li>Maintain active thought leadership e.g., via published papers, presentation at industry conferences, etc.</li></ul></div><div class="rich-text" itemprop="description"><p><strong>Accordant Media</strong>is the largest independent, programmatic media-buying and optimization company in the US. We deliver innovative audience targeting and biddable cross-channel media programs for leading agencies and in-house marketing teams.  Established by digital industry leaders from Avenue A | Razorfish, Aegis Media, Akamai and DoubleClick, Accordant’s one-stop, turnkey service, and proprietary technology built off the Audience OpticsTM system, leverages advanced buying tools integrated with sophisticated multi-screen strategy, data management and cross-channel analytics expertise. </p><p></p><p>Accordant reaches audiences to activate targeted, customized, efficient advertising in a repeatable and scalable manner across paid display, video, mobile, social/Facebook and emerging RTB media channels.  This is done by managing and optimizing advertiser-specific data sets, helping clients achieve more targeted, relevant messages with 100% transparency. Our proprietary system reduces wasted ad impressions, protects advertiser’s data and produces higher engagement and response rates. </p><p></p><p>Co-founded by digital agency execs Art Muldoon and Matt Greitzer, Accordant Media is based in New York City with offices in San Francisco, Chicago and London.</p></div>